The manual, in the section [Linking to an Anchor or Heading|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Working+with+Anchors#WorkingwithAnchors-LinkingtoanAnchororHeading] says.

{quote}
* Note that when linking to a heading, headingname is case-sensitive and must be entered without spaces
* Note that when linking to an anchor, anchorname is case-sensitive, and pagename must be entered with spaces as in the title.
{quote}

That is not entirely accurate as both headingname and anchorname can be entered with or without spaces indistinctly.

