It seems that YouTube has changed how embedded videos can be called. Previously this URL would work fine in the Widget Connector: http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=0z9wAlHeOf4 but now causes an error, instead it needs to have the "feature=player_embedded" argument removed to simply be http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0z9wAlHeOf4

As people potentially have a lot of videos using the old syntax, we should update the Widget Connector to deal with this internally.
